Odaily Planet Daily News: OpenAI founder Sam Altman wrote that the new version of GPT-4o is particularly good at coding, following instructions, and freedom. Previously, OpenAI wrote that GPT-4o was updated again in ChatGPT, and the new changes are as follows: 
Better at following detailed instructions, especially prompts with multiple requests; 
Improved ability to handle complex technical and coding problems; ·Enhanced intuition and creativity; 
Reduce the use of emoticons.
